          "settings": {
            "question": "Which finger should I wear it on?",
            "answer": "<p>The index or middle finger works best. Keep it off the pinky on your writing hand — it moves too much at night. The ring should feel snug but not tight.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_2": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is there really no subscription?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, really. You pay once and you own it all — the ring, the app, and your data. Oura charges $5.99 a month. We never charge you again. Your health data belongs to you.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_3": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I find my ring size?",
            "answer": "<p>Wrap a thin strip of paper around the finger you will wear it on. Mark where it overlaps and measure in millimetres. Most people wear a size 10 on their index finger. Use the size guide above for the full chart.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_4": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I wear it in the shower or pool?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. The N°01 is safe in the shower, pool, and sauna. Do not use it for scuba diving or jet skiing.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_5": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How accurate is the sleep tracking?",
            "answer": "<p>The ring tracks your heart rate and blood oxygen all night. It can tell the difference between light sleep, deep sleep, and dream sleep. It will not replace a sleep study, but it shows your patterns every single night.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_6": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What's the battery life like in real use?",
            "answer": "<p>Up to 7 days on one charge. Most people charge it every 5 to 6 days. It takes about 60 to 90 minutes to charge. Charge it at breakfast — you will never miss a night of data.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_7": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is my health data private?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. Your data stays on your phone. We do not sell it to anyone. Your health info is yours. Always.</p>"
          }
        }
